%h1 Field Placements
- @placements.each do |p|
  %table.table.table-hover
    %tr
      %td Day
      %td= p.day.capitalize
    %tr
      %td Time
      %td
        ="#{p.start_time.strftime("%l:%M %p")} to #{p.end_time.strftime("%l:%M %p")}"
    %tr 
      %td Course
      %td= p.course.name
    %tr 
      %td Grade
      %td= p.course.grade
    %tr 
      %td School Name
      %td= "#{p.mentor_teacher.school.name}"
    %tr 
      %td School Level
      %td= "#{p.mentor_teacher.school.level}"
    %tr
      %td Mentor Teacher
      %td= p.mentor_teacher.user.name
